From hugh at mimosa.com  Tue Dec 16 18:06:19 2014
From: hugh at mimosa.com (D. Hugh Redelmeier)
Date: Tue, 16 Dec 2014 13:06:19 -0500 (EST)
Subject: [GTALUG] Python 2 vs python 3 debate
In-Reply-To: <20141216165741.GN24111@csclub.uwaterloo.ca>
References: <20141216153104.6037651.90559.10974@gmail.com>
 <20141216165741.GN24111@csclub.uwaterloo.ca>
