From opengeometry at yahoo.ca  Wed Dec 17 23:30:48 2014
From: opengeometry at yahoo.ca (William Park)
Date: Wed, 17 Dec 2014 18:30:48 -0500
Subject: [GTALUG] FYI... Adata 16GB microSD = fast read
Message-ID: <20141217233048.GA31944@node1.localdomain>

FYI... I was trying out my new ODROID-U3 with 16GB Adata microSD,
    http://www.canadacomputers.com/product_info.php?cPath=11_1216_175_177&item_id=058665
I was actually looking for 8GB one, but they were out of it.

Adata specs says
    - 10MB/s write -- I got 13MB/s, so it's in the ballpark.
    - 30MB/s read -- I got 80MB/s.  It may go higher, but probably
      limited by my card reader.  It's rare to see something above
      published specs.
-- 
William


